<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/api.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/commonWindow.css">
    <title>宝宝评语</title>
    <style>
        .bg{
            width:100%;
            height:64px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .bg>img{
            width:100%;
            height:64px;
        }
        .comment-detail{
            width:100%;
            height:auto;
            background:#FFFFFF;
            padding-left:18px;
            padding-right:18px;
            padding-bottom:17px;                        
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border-bottom:1px solid #EFEFEF;
            position: relative;
        }
        .comment-detail>.teacher-info{
            width:100%;
            height:auto;
            padding-top:20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .comment-detail>.teacher-info .info-left{
            float:left;
        }
        .comment-detail>.teacher-info .info-left>img{
            width:34px;
            height:34px;
            border-radius:50%;
        }
        .comment-detail>.teacher-info .info-right{
            width:100%;
            padding-left:44px;
            font-size:12px;
            color:#929292;
            letter-spacing: 0.16px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .comment-detail>.teacher-info .info-right .teacher-name{
            line-height:18px;
        }
        .comment-detail>.teacher-info .info-right .comment-time>:nth-child(2){
            margin-left:4.5px;
        }
        .comment-detail .comment-content{
            clear:left;
            margin-top:12px;
        }
        .comment-detail .comment-content .teacher-text{
            width:100%;
            padding:10px 18px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #505050;
            letter-spacing: 0.69px;
            line-height: 22px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 6px 0 rgba(90,200,225,0.30);
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        } 
        .comment-detail .comment-content .parent-reply{
            width:68%;
            height:auto;
            margin:0 auto;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .comment-detail .comment-content .parent-reply .reply-list{
            width:100%;
            height:auto;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            /* padding:15px 13px 23px 9.5px; */
            padding:16px 18px;
            margin-top:12px;
            margin-bottom:41px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            box-shadow: 0 0 6px 0 rgba(90,200,225,0.30);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .comment-detail .comment-content .parent-reply .reply-list li{
            border-bottom: 1px solid #F0F0F0;
             padding:4px 0px; 
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .comment-detail .comment-content .parent-reply .reply-list>:nth-last-child(1){
            border:none;
        }
        .comment-detail .comment-content .parent-reply .reply-list li .reply-info{
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #505050;
            letter-spacing: 0.6px;
        }
        .comment-detail .comment-content .parent-reply .reply-list li .reply-person{
            margin-top:6px;
        }
        .comment-detail .comment-content .parent-reply .reply-list li .dialog-01{
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #929292;
            letter-spacing: 0.15px;
            line-height: 16px;            
        }
        .comment-detail .comment-content .parent-reply .reply-list li .dialog-02{
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #929292;
            letter-spacing: 0.15px;
            line-height: 16px;                    
        }
        .comment-detail .comment-content .parent-reply .reply-list li .rep{
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #202020;
            letter-spacing: 0.15px;
            line-height: 16px;
            /*margin-left:-8px;*/
            /*margin-right: -8px;*/  
        }
        .c-reply>img{
            width:17px;
            height:18px;
            position:absolute;
            right:61px;
            bottom:20px;
        }
        .c-delete>img{
            width:18px;
            height:18px;
            position:absolute;
            right:18px;
            bottom:20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="main">
        <div id="wrap">
            <div class="bg">
                <img src="../../image/commentbg.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="comment-detail">
                <div class="teacher-info">
                    <div class="info-left">
                        <img src="../../image/teacherAvatar.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-right">
                        <div class="teacher-name">
                            <span>许友珍老师</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="comment-time">
                            <span class="c-date">2018.06.07</span>
                            <span class="c-time">11:13:34</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="comment-content">
                    <div class="teacher-text">
                        <p>于利宏宝宝表现的特别好，帮助同学打扫卫生，希望下周继续努力。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="parent-reply">
                        <ul class="reply-list">
                            <li>
                                <p class="reply-info">谢谢许老师的鼓励，小宏很开心。</p>
                                <p class="reply-person">
                                    <span class="dialog-01">于利宏爸爸</span><span class="rep">回复</span><span class="dialog-02">许友珍老师</span>
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class="reply-info">小宏很乖</p>
                                <p class="reply-person">
                                    <span class="dialog-01">许友珍老师</span><span class="rep">回复</span><span class="dialog-02">于利宏爸爸</span>
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class="reply-info">谢谢夸奖</p>
                                <p class="reply-person">
                                    <span class="dialog-01">于利宏爸爸</span><span class="rep">回复</span><span class="dialog-02">许友珍老师</span>
                                </p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="comment-operate">
                    <div class="c-reply">
                        <img src="../../icon/reply.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="c-delete">
                        <img src="../../icon/delete.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="comment-detail">
                    <div class="teacher-info">
                        <div class="info-left">
                            <img src="../../image/teacherAvatar.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="info-right">
                            <div class="teacher-name">
                                <span>许友珍老师</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="comment-time">
                                <span class="c-date">2018.06.07</span>
                                <span class="c-time">11:13:34</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="comment-content">
                        <div class="teacher-text">
                            <p>李小明宝宝把自己的玩具给其它小朋友们分享，做的很棒。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>    
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/api.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/mui.min.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/util.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/kv.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/apiCloud.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="./script/init.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/template-native.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/data.js"></script>
    <script>
        
    </script>
</body>
</html>